m children or knowingly market to children. Therefore, in accordance with the U.S. Children’s Online Privacy Protection Act, if we receive actual knowledge that anyone under the age of 13 has provided personal information to us without the requisite and verifiable parental consent, we will delete that information from the Services as quickly as is reasonably practical.\\u003c/bdt\\u003e\\u003c/bdt\\u003e\\u003cbdt class=\\\"statement-end-if-in-editor\\\" data-type=\\\"close\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan style=\\\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 16.8667px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\\\"\\u003e\\u003cbdt class=\\\"statement-end-if-in-editor\\\"\\u003e\\u003c/bdt\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/bdt\\u003e\\u003c/bdt\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/div\\u003e\\u003cdiv class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"line-height: 1.5;\\\"\\u003e\\u003cbr\\u003e\\u003c/div\\u003e\\u003cdiv class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"line-height: 1.5;\\\"\\u003e\\u003cbdt class=\\\"block-container if\\\" data-type=\\\"if\\\" style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\"\\u003e\\u003cbdt class=\\\"statement-end-if-in-editor\\\" data-type=\\\"close\\\"\\u003e\\u003c/bdt\\u003e\\u003c/bdt\\u003e\\u003cbdt class=\\\"block-container if\\\" data-type=\\\"if\\\"\\u003e\\u003cbdt data-type=\\\"conditional-block\\\"\\u003e\\u003cbdt class=\\\"block-component\\\" data-record-question-key=\\\"privacy_policy_followup\\\" data-type=\\\"statement\\\" style=\\\"font-size: 14.6667px;\\\"\\u003e\\u003c/bdt\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/bdt\\u003e\\u003c/bdt\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/bdt\\u003e\\u003c/bdt\\u003e\\u003c/bdt\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/bdt\\u003e\\u003c/bdt\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/bdt\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/bdt\\u003e\\u003c/bdt\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/bdt\\u003e\\u003c/bdt\\u003e\\u003c/bdt\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/bdt\\u003e\\u003c/bdt\\u003e\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/div\\u003e\\u003cdiv class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"line-height: 1.5;\\\"\\u003e\\u003cbdt class=\\\"b